<title>Summoner</title>
<!--#include virtual="/content_header.html" -->
<div class="page_title">Summoner</div>
Fought during <a href="/chapters/chapter_two.html#blizzard_p">Chapter Two</a> in the <a href="/settings/blizzard.html">Blizzard</a>.</br>
The Summoner does not do any fighting of it's own.</br>
It traps it's enemies in a blizzard enclosed in a large ice dome.</br>
It summons <a href="/monsters/ice_wolf.html">Ice Wolves</a> and <a href="/monsters/ice_golem.html">Ice Golems</a> to fight for it.</br>
When in danger the Summoner will rapidly summon Ice Golems between it and the attacker.</br>
Upon death, the Summoner shatters.</br>
It's dying breath can severly cripple whomever dealt the killing blow.</br>
Without the Summoner to maintain the winds, the blizzard dies down.</br>
After the blizzard dies down the dome will shatter.</br>
